	n : Insulin (Human) R
	Indications : Diabetic ketoacidosis, Diabetes mellitus
	Doses and administration : Adult: SC DM Dosage should be individualised and adjusted based on patient's glycaemic response. Usual range: 0.5-1 u/kg/day.
									
