	n : Aluminium Hydroxide + Magnesium Hydroxide + Simethicon
	Indications : Dyspepsia, Flatulence
	Doses and administration : Adult: PO Antacid Up to 1 g/day. Hyperphosphataemia in chronic renal failure Up to 10 g/day in divided doses w/ meals.
	Contara-indications : Hypersensitivity to aluminium salts.
	Side effects : Constipation; intestinal obstruction (with large doses); phosphate depletion may occur with prolonged admin or large doses.
